entry.value: UPDATE weather_data SET ${field_name} = '${${field_name}:replaceNull('NULL')}' WHERE observation_date = '${observation_date}' AND observation_time = '${observation_time}' AND location_name = '${location_name}'

SELECT observation_date, observation_time, location_name, ${field_name} FROM weather_data_meteostat WHERE observation_date = '${observation_date}' AND observation_time = '${observation_time}' AND location_name = '${location_name}'

UPDATE weather_data SET lightning = 'True' WHERE observation_date = '${observation_date}' AND extract(hour from observation_time) = extract(hour from '${observation_time}'::time) AND location_name = '${location_name}'

INSERT INTO weather_data ( observation_date, observation_time, location_name, technology, longitude, latitude, snow, ice, temperature_c, windspeed_m_s, windgusts_m_s, visibility_km, original_source) VALUES ( '${observation_date}' ,'${observation_time}' ,'${location_name}' ,'${technology}' ,${longitude:replaceNull('NULL')} ,${latitude:replaceNull('NULL')} ,'${snow:replaceNull('NULL')}' ,'${ice:replaceNull('NULL')}' ,${temperature_c:replaceNull('NULL')} ,${windspeed_m_s:replaceNull('NULL')} ,${windgusts_m_s:replaceNull('NULL')} ,${visibility_km:replaceNull('NULL')} ,'Visual Crossing' ) ON CONFLICT ON CONSTRAINT unique_timestamp_and_location DO UPDATE SET snow = '${snow:replaceNull('NULL')}', ice = '${ice:replaceNull('NULL')}', temperature_c = ${temperature_c:replaceNull('NULL')}, windspeed_m_s = ${windspeed_m_s:replaceNull('NULL')}, windgusts_m_s = ${windgusts_m_s:replaceNull('NULL')}, visibility_km = ${visibility_km:replaceNull('NULL')}, original_source = 'Visual Crossing'

UPDATE weather_data SET ${field_name} = ${${field_name}:replaceNull('NULL')} WHERE observation_date = '${observation_date}' AND observation_time = '${observation_time}' AND location_name = '${location_name}'

INSERT INTO weather_data ( observation_date, observation_time, location_name, technology, longitude, latitude, snow, ice, temperature_c, windspeed_m_s, windgusts_m_s, visibility_km, original_source) VALUES ( '${observation_date}' ,'${observation_time}' ,'${location_name}' ,'${technology}' ,${longitude:replaceNull('NULL')} ,${latitude:replaceNull('NULL')} ,'${snow:replaceNull('NULL')}' ,'${ice:replaceNull('NULL')}' ,${temperature_c:replaceNull('NULL')} ,${windspeed_m_s:replaceNull('NULL')} ,${windgusts_m_s:replaceNull('NULL')} ,${visibility_km:replaceNull('NULL')} ,'Meteostat' ) ON CONFLICT ON CONSTRAINT unique_timestamp_and_location DO NOTHING
